                <note rend="inline" type="source">882.51/1016b: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Liberia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-11-19T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 19, 1919, 5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>It is understood that receivership depositary agreement with Bank of British West
                    Africa expired November 11 but continues in force subject to termination by
                    three months’ notice on either side.</p>
                <p>If Bank serves notice notify Department.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
